<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Вход - Личный кабинет</title>
    <link href="../static/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    </head>
<body>
    <div class="login-card text-center">
        <div class="logo">
            <p class="bi bi-mortarboard-fill"></p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="mb-2">Личный кабинет</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">Система онлайн-обучения LMS</p>
        
        <a href="/account/api/v1/auth/login" class="btn btn-keycloak w-100">
            <p class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-2"></p>Войти через Keycloak
        </a>
        
        <div class="mt-3">
            <a href="/account/register" class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100">
                <p class="bi bi-person-plus me-2"></p>Зарегистрироваться
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="divider">
            <span>информация</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="features text-start">
            <h6 class="mb-3"><p class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></p>Возможности кабинета:</h6>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <p class="bi bi-graph-up"></p>
                <span>Отслеживание прогресса обучения</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <p class="bi bi-award"></p>
                <span>Управление сертификатами</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <p class="bi bi-calendar-check"></p>
                <span>История посещений уроков</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <p class="bi bi-person-gear"></p>
                <span>Настройки профиля</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>